snippet.title: The Void Project | Steam Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
Hey everyone! We're super excited to show you a sneak peek of our new game! Even with everyone talking about GTA, we couldn't wait to give you a taste of what we're making in our studio. Timing might seem odd, but good things sometimes surprise us! 🌟

And guess what? We've also released our first-ever game's Steam Page You can add it to your wishlist here: Steam/The Void Project
